Titolo: Battlezone (2016 video game)

Anno: 2016

Descrizione: Battlezone is an arcade game released by Rebellion in 2016. It is an update of the original 1980 arcade game.  The game was one of the launch titles for PlayStation VR in October 2016.
As with the original, the game features first-person tank combat against an AI-controlled enemy force, but includes co-operative multiplayer and a campaign structure, together with being designed for virtual reality.

Genere: Vehicular combat

Valutazione: N/A
